title: URF Icons
body: When I bought some URF icons earlier I didn't get any. Any reason why? I just really hope I didn't waste my money. {{sticker:zombie-nunu-bummed}}

replies.body: Did the Icons ever show up? I wasn't able to find anything off on your account, so if you're still having issues, reach out in a [**support ticket**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) so we can help out!
